  "description": "A breathtaking panoramic view of a city nestled beside a wide bay, bathed in the warm, golden light of a setting sun. The sun itself is visible as a bright orb just above the horizon, creating a strong reflection on the water. Above the sun are dramatic, layered clouds painted with hues of orange, yellow, and deep red. Below, the city sprawls out with numerous buildings and streets, creating a dense urban landscape. In the foreground, lush green trees and foliage frame the scene, adding depth and a natural element. The overall composition captures a sense of grandeur and tranquility.",
